definitions.definition: Any person (especially a woman ) who has sexual intercourse or engages in other sexual activity for payment , especially as a means of livelihood.
A woman who has sexual intercourse or engages in other sexual activity for payment , especially as a means of livelihood.
A person who does, or offers to do, a demeaning or dishonourable activity for money or personal gain; someone who acts in a dishonourable way for personal advantage.

main_definition: Any person (especially a woman ) who has sexual intercourse or engages in other sexual activity for payment , especially as a means of livelihood. [from 18th c.]
